<br>
While I'm not certain of the standards for a summary judgement with regards to claims of libel, my gut feeling is that this suit might have a more difficult time passing summary judgement.  Should it, though, I would suggest the old standard of &quot;It isn't libel if its true&quot; comes fairly well into play.<br>
<br>
As to whether Verant/SOE begin to sue us...whyever would they?  We're still playing their game and paying their salaries, so to speak. =D<br>
